The evidence with the title 'Newt Gingrich supported an Individual Mandate as recently as may ... ' says Jan 30, 2012  ... This clip really should dispel once and for all any questions over Gingrich 's support for a national health-insurance mandate. Somewhat strangely he's never really denied supporting the mandate, and in fact as late as may of last year reiterated essentially the same position on Meet The Press. 
